	<h1 class="title">iPad 将人们使用电脑的年龄降低到了 1 岁</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1375/small/1375.jpg?1460641790" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐弢 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-07-06 13:34:03 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11680/medium/11680.jpg?1436637533" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


